title: i am way over level seven and  am very confused need help
body: i am trying to make a comment on a post and it will not let me because it says im not level seven

replies.body: Heya, sometimes your profile just needs to sync up.  Your post here should have done that, but you can use this[ syncing tool ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool)as well!
